---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
import { SITE } from '../utils/seo';
---

<Page
  title="DMCA Policy"
  description="DMCA takedown policy for superbearadventuremod.io. Learn how to submit a copyright infringement notice."
  headerIcon='<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3" /></svg>'
  headerGradient="from-red-700 to-red-900"
>
  <p>
    superbearadventuremod.io respects the intellectual property rights of others. If you believe that any content on this website infringes upon your copyright, please follow the procedures outlined below.
  </p>

  <h2>Filing a DMCA Takedown Notice</h2>
  <p>If you are a copyright owner or authorized agent and believe that content on this site infringes your copyright, please send a written notice including:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Your physical or electronic signature</li>
    <li>Identification of the copyrighted work(s) you believe has been infringed</li>
    <li>The URL(s) of the infringing content on our site</li>
    <li>Your contact information (name, address, phone number, email)</li>
    <li>A statement that you have a good faith belief that the use is not authorized</li>
    <li>A statement, under penalty of perjury, that the information in your notice is accurate and that you are the copyright owner or authorized to act on their behalf</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Where to Send</h2>
  <p>
    Send your DMCA takedown notice to: <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>
  </p>
  <p>
    We will respond to valid DMCA notices within 48 hours and will remove or disable access to the allegedly infringing content.
  </p>

  <h2>Counter-Notification</h2>
  <p>
    If you believe your content was removed in error, you may submit a counter-notification including similar identifying information and a statement explaining why you believe the removal was a mistake.
  </p>

  <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
  <p>
    superbearadventuremod.io is an independent fan site. All game content, trademarks, and assets belong to their respective owners, including Earthkwak Games. We always encourage users to support the official developers.
  </p>
</Page>
